---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Projects from '../../components/en/Projects.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  locale="en"
  title="Projects"
  description="Selected integration and automation projects with practical impact in day-to-day operations."
>
  <main class="page" id="main-content">
    <section class="page-intro">
      <p class="eyebrow">Case Examples</p>
      <h1>Projects with clear operational impact</h1>
      <p class="muted">
        The focus is on stable interfaces, traceable processes, and planned evolution of existing
        systems.
      </p>
    </section>

    <Projects />
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
